      "text": [
        "2583 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «يُكْرَهُ لِلرَّجُلِ أَنْ يُجِيبَ بِالتَّلْبِيَةِ إِذَا نُودِيَ وَ هُوَ مُحْرِمٌ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2583 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"It is disliked for a man to respond with the Talbiyah when he is called while in the state of Ihram.\""
        ]
      }
    }
